<th colspan="2" style="text-align:center">Notes</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center">
<div style="text-align: left;">
<p>(1) Rust's secured the part of 24-year-old attorney Hank Tabor on <a href="/wiki/NBC" title="NBC">NBC</a>'s <i><a href="/wiki/Sam_Benedict" title="Sam Benedict">Sam Benedict</a></i> with <a href="/wiki/Edmond_O%27Brien" title="Edmond O'Brien">Edmond O'Brien</a> by winning the part over sixty competitors based on his acting experience and his educational background.</p>
<p>(2) Rust was reared by an aunt because his mother died when he was five, and his father was a United States Navy officer.</p>
(3) Several years before <i>Sam Benedict</i>, Rust acted on stage with <a href="/wiki/Fredric_March" title="Fredric March">Fredric March</a> in <a href="/wiki/Eugene_O%27Neill" title="Eugene O'Neill">Eugene O'Neill</a>'s <i><a href="/wiki/Long_Day%27s_Journey_into_Night" title="Long Day's Journey into Night">Long Day's Journey into Night</a></i>.</div>
</td>
